window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>After 20 years away from Kragdon-ah, Alex Hawk and his daughters return to the future.</b></p> <p>They find invaders with guns in great numbers. Now, Alex will take the fight to those invaders in their own homeland. He must face a superior force with more advanced technology. The battle will be for the very soul of Kragdon-ah. Can Alex Hawk and his mighty dog Monda-ak survive their greatest challenge?</p> <p><i>Prince of Kragdon-ah</i> is the fifth book in Alex Hawk Time Travel Adventure, an action-packed time-travel/portal fiction series.</p> <p><i>Includes a special note from the author.</i></p>"; 
